<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Binance Receipt</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: rgb(18, 184, 54);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header .logo {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .header .subtitle {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .body {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .body p {
            margin: 0 0 10px;
        }
        .body .username {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .body .emailbody {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .body ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .body ul li {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .body ul li span {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .contact {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .contact h5 {
            margin: 0 10px 0 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .contact a {
            color: rgb(18, 184, 54);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .footer {
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <p class="logo">Team 71</p>
            <p class="subtitle">Proper IT Solution</p>
        </div>
        <div class="body">
            <p class="username">Hi <%=username%>,</p>
            <p class="emailbody">
                Thank you for using our service.<br>
                Recently you made a payment using Binance Pay. We are confirming that we have received your payment.<br>
                Here is the summary of your payment:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li><span>Plan:</span> <%=plan%></li>
                <li><span>Trx Id:</span> <%=merchantTradeNo%></li>
                <li><span>Currency:</span> <%=currency%></li>
                <li><span>Amount:</span> <%=orderAmount%></li>
            </ul>
            <p class="emailbody">
                If you have any questions, feel free to contact us.
            </p>
            <div class="contact">
                <h5>Contact on WhatsApp:</h5>
                <a href="https://wa.me/+8801738619197">Click here</a>
            </div>
            <p class="emailbody">
                Best regards,<br>
                <span class="company">Team 71</span>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Team 71. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
